<br>
I felt really great with this catch. While heading back to base camp (the smuggler's outpost). I happened upon a delirous merek avenger lair with a baby. Slowly i creep toward it, this time there is only 1 adult guarding the lair (lucky me!) and a baby. I mask scented and try to tame.... first try ... fail. Second try fail .... after my 12th try... succeed! Yey! Now I got myself a toxic merek battlelord and a delirious merek avenger all in one run :).<br>
<br>
The trick here? Seperate the baby from the adult as this will greatly enhance your survival rate. How to do that? Well if your tame critical fails, the baby aggros you right? Make sure your weapon is unequipped and just let the baby hit you (hopefully no adult is nearby), simply let it hit you while you stim up and drag  the baby far away. With a little bit of patience you can drag the baby as far as 128m away from it's lair. But babies has this habbit of returning to its mommy, the way to stop it is to simply tame it before they run all the way back coz once you initiate the taming sequence the baby will stop moving and turn to face you. It's like fishing really, reel em in, release a bit, reel them in even closer..etc till u get them. It's important not to panic and watch where you are going if something is chasing you. Always plan an escape route. Nothing is worse than having run into another aggresive creature lair while running away from something chasing you.  Another lesson learned during this trip, some creatures are aggressive to each other. Example: merek battlelords are aggressive to creatures like Robas. What happened was, I observed some merek battlelords wandered into a roba lair (yes there are robas now in Endor). It sparked a huge battle between the robas and battlelords. It ended having half a dozen robas killed while the battlelord only have some minor damage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm14.showNextMessage?topicID=9.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.